<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">RADLib<sp/>includes<sp/>a<sp/>CMake-invoked<sp/>Python<sp/>generator<sp/>for<sp/>compact<sp/>binary<sp/>TCP<sp/>protocols.</highlight></codeline>
